{"tid":2029522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市場反應開始浮現，勿做投共狗趁低吸納","createTime":"2020-05-22T09:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T13:03:38.000Z","uid":199769,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc05bf8b41d731c57cd6c47f43ea5b5403f50a8","tid":2029522,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"如果見股票急跌而趁低吸納，我可以話你知<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同投共、出賣手足無分別</span></span></strong>。大家咁努力用市場同經濟迫緊中共，對家開始行到國安法，大家終於準備攬炒。你同我趁低吸納，趁機搵錢，根本就發國難財，同時幫緊中共喺低位托市。仍然代表緊香港市場仲可以若無其事咁搵錢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句講哂，由得個股市下跌到零。唔好趁低吸納，唔好幫中共托市，唔好幫中共穩定市場，唔好為市場賦予希望。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲抱住發財嘅心，就唔好談什麼時代革命。"},{"pid":"53f4edf9c1a4a7b47f1865352e9025a60ecd988f","tid":2029522,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"趁低吸納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低處未算低啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0440c1e9e72af2fb95b2d51709fb56748d86b8cd","tid":2029522,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"諗太多<br />\n事實上港豬多過黃"},{"pid":"7166a3c4d816b8e91c17bb47c36e2a5b6f5ae51d","tid":2029522,"uid":199769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53f4edf9c1a4a7b47f1865352e9025a60ecd988f","tid":2029522,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"趁低吸納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低處未算低啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hk